Vocals: Meenakshy Jyothish
Music arrangement : Priyan Rajmohan
Original Song by : AR Rahman Sir.

Am so happy to collab with Priyan (@rowdy.records ) and present to you “Snehithaney” from Alaipayuthey by AR Rahman sir. 
Priyan has been doing his own music through compositions and has also uploaded his tracks on Spotify! So do check him out! 
This is also done as an initiative by @nus_ics for the foreign workers living in PGPR of NUS.

#staysafe #stayhomesg #music #cover #coversong #tamilsong #arr #arrahman #migrantworkers
